title: Tribute to the Headhunterz by whis.mp3
description:
Because he makes what I like to call "the best hardstyle" at the moment, I couldn&#039;t resist making a remix of all the best songs he created. And because I don&#039;t like very long songs and just a short climax, I tried to keep some speed in the mix.

I hope you&#039;ll enjoy it, please leave a comment with your opinion!

Trackz:
1. Digiwave
2. Forever az One
3. Scar Ur Face
4. Speakafreak
5. End of My Existence
6. Rock Civilization
7. Scantraxx rootz

P.s. Of course all kudo&#039;s go to mister Headhunter himself, but if you happen to have some left, please remember me ;)
